\sum_n^\infty (-1)^n\frac{\sin^2 n}n
\begin{array}{lcl}\sum_{n=1}^N (-1)^n\sin^2 n &= & \sum_{n=1}^N (-1)^{n+1} \frac{e^{2in}-2+e^{-2in}}{4}\\ & = &\sum_{n=1}^N \frac{(-1)^{n+1}}{4}e^{2in} -2\sum_{n=1}^N \frac{(-1)^{n+1}}{4} +\sum_{n=1}^N \frac{(-1)^{n+1}}{4}e^{-2in} \end{array}
a_n = \frac 1 n
b_n =(-1)^{n+1} \frac{e^{2in}}{4}
\sum_{n=1}^M b_n 
-e^{2i}
\frac{e^{2i}}{4} \frac{(-1)^M e^{2iM}-1}{-e^{2i}-1}
|\sum_{n=1}^M b_n|<2
M
